	[lib] Move svz_{malloc,realloc,free}_func behind ‘svz_set_mm_funcs’.

	* serveez-api.texi.in (Memory management): Delete
	‘svz_malloc_func’, ‘svz_realloc_func’, ‘svz_free_func’;
	add ‘svz_set_mm_funcs’.

