	proof-reading.  Thanks!

2002-10-01  Stefan Jahn  <stefan@lkcc.org>

	* serveez-doc-snarf.awk: Replaced `> "/dev/stderr"' by
	`| "cat 1>&2"'.  This is useful for platforms where the
	device file "/dev/stderr" does not exist.

